Anyways. Another reason I'm thinking why KD was saying what he was saying, along with the "agenda," was because the year before that, you had the NBA media pushing that narrative and hoping and begging to see LBJ vs. Kobe in the finals. The very next year, again they were pushing for LBJ to make it to the Finals, but the NBA didn't want to make the same mistake like the year prior, so it was more hush hush, but they certainly wanted to try and get LBJ and Kobe again.
